name: A Z U R A D R A G O N
description: Azura the dragon is my work of fiction which is a female warrior in a wolf mask with a cybepunk concept who is a time traveler. Together with his cyborg dragon, he travels through time to kill his enemy, the king of darkness who wants to rule the universe and turn the universe into a hell for mankind. will he succeed in defeating the king of darkness. Let's continue with my story.
